c.co.uk/bbctrust/governance/regulatory_framework/charter_agreement.html"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">www.bbc.co.uk/bbctrust/governance/regulatory_framework/charter_agreement.html</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn4"></a><a href="#_ftnref4">[4]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">BBC Framework Agreement</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">clause </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">85: “General provisions about arr</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">angement</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">s made under clauses 83 and 84</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn5"></a><a href="#_ftnref5">[5]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Putting Quality First, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">BBC Strategy Review, BBC</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">’s</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> Proposals to the BBC Trust, March 2010.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn6"></a><a href="#_ftnref6">[6]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">BBC Training: </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Observations on the Current Operation and Effectiveness of the BBC’s Arrangements for the Training and Retraining of </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">BBC Staff</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">, BBC Trust, June 2010</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn7"></a><a href="#_ftnref7">[7]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> See <